41:45.357 --> 41:47.191
He's not what I
imagined for you.

41:49.896 --> 41:50.895
Violinist.

41:54.901 --> 41:56.167
What did you imagine?

41:58.037 --> 41:59.853
I don't know.

41:59.855 --> 42:01.672
Oh, he's kind, and smart.

42:02.942 --> 42:04.108
A genius, actually.

42:06.613 --> 42:08.579
