my name down on the form.

42:18.592 --> 42:19.658
I didn't put your name down

42:19.660 --> 42:22.060
- on a form.
- Yes, you did.

42:22.062 --> 42:23.428
I don't know why
you keep saying.

42:23.430 --> 42:26.098
I didn't put your name
down, I didn't do that.

42:26.100 --> 42:27.599
There were no forms!

42:27.601 --> 42:29.968
- Stop acting like this.
- Acting like what?

42:29.970 --> 42:31.703
Like you had a choice.

42:31.705 --> 42:33.488
Whether you put my
name down or not,

42:33.490 --> 42:35.275
- you had nowhere to go.
- There were so many places

42:35.277 --> 42:36.567
- I could've gone.
- Where?

42:36.569 --> 42:37.859
Your apartment, your
apartment in New York.

42:37.861 --> 42:39.151
You would've
been alone at my apartment.

42:39.153 --> 42:40.444
- I'm alone here!
- No, you're not!

42:43.451 --> 42:48.588
I'm here.

42:54.362 --> 42:56.211
I'm here.

43:09.378 --> 43:10.377
John!

43:12.548 --> 43:13.547
John!

43:16.986 --> 43:19.320
And there you are.

43:19.322 --> 43:21.255
- Thanks again.
- Thank you for staying

43:21.257 --> 43:22.490
at the Indian Princess Inn.

43:22.492 --> 43:23.908
Take care.

43:23.910 --> 43:25.327
- Have a good honeymoon.
- Thanks.

45:18.412 --> 45:19.411
Hey.

45:22.784 --> 45:24.284
Hey.

48:29.978 --> 48:32.979
We're gonna be
gone for five days.

48:33.850 --> 48:36.517
I think it'll be good for us.

48:38.521 --> 48:39.787
For all of us.

48:56.839 --> 49:00.475
We're in the middle of the
fucking wilderness, Louise.

49:02.846 --> 49:06.081
I mean, I could've
just stayed at the inn.

49:06.083 --> 49:07.449
Yeah, you could've.

49:09.953 --> 49:13.488
But I can't be alone, right?

49:14.425 --> 49:15.991
I'm like a danger to myself.

49:17.728 --> 49:19.461
Isn't that what they tell you?

49:21.866 --> 49:22.932
You know what?

49:24.369 --> 49:25.501
You got in the car.

49:25.503 --> 49:28.504
You got in the car and
you got on the plane

49:28.506 --> 49:30.106
because guess what, Isabella?

49:32.043 --> 49:33.042
You need me.

49:38.383 --> 49:40.049
After all this time,
I'm the only thing

49:40.051 --> 49:41.117
you've got left.

49:48.561 --> 49:49.560
You're scared.

49:51.897 --> 49:53.430
- What?
- Yeah.

49:54.834 --> 49:57.401
You're scared
because you're lost.

51:03.639 --> 51:04.905
It's not that easy
for me, you know,

51:04.907 --> 51:08.175
just to put my
life back together.

51:09.812 --> 51:11.878
I don't need you to
remind me about it.

51:11.880 --> 51:12.879
I know.

51:15.017 --> 51:16.016
I know.

51:18.787 --> 51:19.786
I'm sorry.

51:32.635 --> 51:34.602
Do you love him?

51:34.604 --> 51:37.138
Of course.

51:37.140 --> 51:38.706
Of course I do.

51:42.512 --> 51:43.678
It's just that sometimes I think

51:43.680 --> 51:45.012
he loves it more than me.

51:45.850 --> 51:46.815
What?

51:47.852 --> 51:48.817
The violin.

51:51.655 --> 51:53.555
He's under so much pressure.

51:54.792 --> 51:56.091
I try to understand.

51:58.496 --> 52:00.028
I told him not to bring it

52:00.030 --> 52:01.563
or he's gonna practice
like every day.

52:04.668 --> 52:06.869
I don't think he's had
the chance to here.

52:13.011 --> 52:14.544
I saw him.

52:14.546 --> 52:15.545
What?

52:16.748 --> 52:19.782
I saw him playing.

52:20.552 --> 52:23.052
When?

52:23.054 --> 52:24.888
It was at the inn.

52:24.890 --> 52:26.222
I was walking and...

52:26.224 --> 52:28.858
What are you talking about?

52:56.889 --> 53:01.226
Did you play for her?

53:01.228 --> 53:02.761
Isabella?

53:02.763 --> 53:03.762
When?

53:04.665 --> 53:05.864
At the inn.

53:09.603 --> 53:11.303
She said you played for her.

53:11.305 --> 53:13.605
I didn't play for her.

53:23.618 --> 53:24.617
Maybe she saw me.

53:25.620 --> 53:26.686
The door was open.

53:27.622 --> 53:28.754
I didn't play for her.

53:28.756 --> 53:29.889
I mean, it could've
been anybody.

53:34.262 --> 53:35.761
So it doesn't
matter when I'm there?

53:36.664 --> 53:37.964
Of course it matters.

53:37.966 --> 53:39.966
It's different,
though, you're my wife.

55:01.319 --> 55:03.086
It's not that deep.

55:04.690 --> 55:07.190
I don't
wanna get in the water.

55:07.192 --> 55:09.725
It kinda defeats the purpose

55:09.727 --> 55:12.261
of us walking all this way if
you don't get in the water.

55:12.264 --> 55:14.698
I don't care, I
don't wanna get in.

59:02.604 --> 59:04.103
Where were you?

59:18.687 --> 59:20.186
John, where were you?

59:33.002 --> 59:35.970
Louise,
Louise, sorry, wait, wait!

59:41.410 --> 59:42.409
- Wait, wait!
- No!

59:42.411 --> 59:44.411
Louise, stop, stop!

59:45.515 --> 59:46.481
Louise!

01:00:09.273 --> 01:00:10.673
Louise.

01:00:10.675 --> 01:00:11.674
Louise.

01:00:11.676 --> 01:00:13.108
- Do something!
- I don't know what you

01:00:13.110 --> 01:00:14.543
want me to do!

01:00:15.546 --> 01:00:16.612
Okay, okay.

01:00:52.751 --> 01:00:53.717
Hold this.

01:00:56.088 --> 01:00:58.222
- Louise.
- Don't move her.

01:00:59.626 --> 01:01:00.564
Louise, wake up.

01:01:00.566 --> 01:01:01.504
- Can I pick her up?
- Don't touch her,

01:01:01.506 --> 01:01:02.444
don't move her, don't move her.

01:01:02.446 --> 01:01:03.384
Louise, it's me.

01:01:03.386 --> 01:01:04.325
Don't fucking touch her!

01:01:30.124 --> 01:01:31.723
Look, we can't just sit here.

01:01:33.127 --> 01:01:34.126
We can't do this.

01:01:35.563 --> 01:01:36.662
- It's too late.
- It's too late?

01:01:36.664 --> 01:01:38.097
Yeah, it's too fucking late.

01:01:38.099 --> 01:01:39.631
It's too late for what?

01:01:39.633 --> 01:01:42.367
To get help, I mean, we
can't do anything for her.

01:01:42.369 --> 01:01:44.571
- Look at her.
- What are you talking about?

01:01:44.573 --> 01:01:45.755
What do you mean what am I

01:01:45.757 --> 01:01:46.939
- talking about?
- She's getting worse.

01:01:46.941 --> 01:01:48.123
- What are you talking about?
- One of us needs to go

01:01:48.125 --> 01:01:49.308
for help.

01:03:11.930 --> 01:03:16.432
Louise, she was the
special kid, you know?

01:03:20.739 --> 01:03:22.639
She always made people smile.

01:03:33.652 --> 01:03:35.285
Mom left when we were young.

01:03:37.623 --> 01:03:39.456
I don't know, I guess two girls

01:03:40.759 --> 01:03:43.894
was to much for our dad.

01:03:43.896 --> 01:03:46.931
He didn't really know
what to do with us.

01:03:52.339 --> 01:03:53.338
And, you know,

01:03:55.842 --> 01:03:59.377
she wanted to swim.

01:04:02.582 --> 01:04:06.818
We had this big pool
in our backyard.

01:04:16.931 --> 01:04:18.664
One day, I wanted to teach her.

01:04:22.303 --> 01:04:24.670
I was old enough to
know what I was doing.

01:04:35.350 --> 01:04:37.684
I put her head under water.

01:04:41.523 --> 01:04:43.023
Her lungs filled with water,

01:04:48.363 --> 01:04:50.563
and she couldn't breathe.

01:04:54.670 --> 01:04:55.669
Our dad,

01:04:58.374 --> 01:05:02.743
he got home just in time,

01:05:06.049 --> 01:05:08.416
just in time to save her.

01:05:13.856 --> 01:05:16.590
I don't talk about that a lot.

01:05:19.529 --> 01:05:23.732
I mean, I think about it.

01:05:35.946 --> 01:05:37.846
I hadn't talked
to her in so long.

01:05:42.986 --> 01:05:44.987
She contacted me when she...

01:05:46.691 --> 01:05:47.890
She came to see me.

01:05:54.766 --> 01:05:56.499
It'd been a while.

01:06:05.410 --> 01:06:06.709
She told me about you.

01:06:13.919 --> 01:06:15.619
And it made sense,

01:06:21.193 --> 01:06:22.893
why she chose you.

01:06:28.667 --> 01:06:29.900
I understood.

01:08:40.872 --> 01:08:42.238
Wait.

01:08:42.240 --> 01:08:44.006
Wait, wait, wait,
wait, wait, wait!

01:09:03.261 --> 01:09:04.361
John.

01:09:09.635 --> 01:09:10.133
What is it, what is it,

01:09:10.135 --> 01:09:10.633
- what is it?
- There's somebody.

01:09:10.635 --> 01:09:11.133
What is it, what is it?

01:09:11.135 --> 01:09:11.633
What do you mean,

01:09:11.635 --> 01:09:12.133
- there's a man?
- There's a man.

01:09:12.135 --> 01:09:12.633
Where, where, where?

01:09:12.635 --> 01:09:13.133
- He's over there.
- Why didn't you bring him?

01:09:13.135 --> 01:09:13.633
Why didn't you bring him here?

01:09:13.635 --> 01:09:14.133
Wait!

01:09:14.135 --> 01:09:14.634
We can go.

